Class LevelThree

    public class LevelThree
extends LevelParent
    The LevelThree class extends LevelParent and is the third level in a series of three. The level focuses on online safety as well as the dangers of interacting with strangers.

    Course Info:

    ICS4U0 with Krasteva, V.
    Version:
    0.2
    Author:
    Liam Telenko and Russell Leong
